Basic Usage of Git
1. Relations among remote, repository, index and workspace
	remote to repository:		fetch/clone
	repository to workspace:	checkout
	remote to workspace:		pull
	workspace to index:		add
	index to repository:		commit
	repository to remote:		push
2. git pull
	git pull remote_machine remote_branch:local_branch
	e.g. git pull origin gzh:master
3. git push
	git push remote_machien local_branch:remote_branch
	e.g. git push origin master:gzh

